## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data and the scope of the sources reviewed. While the sources provide a broad overview, they may not capture all nuances of the gender pay gap across different cultures and industries. Additionally, the data is subject to change as new research emerges and societal norms evolve. Further research is needed to explore the intersectionality of race, ethnicity, and other factors in the gender pay gap.